    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "RE: AERIAL PHENOMENON RESEARCH GROUP",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "MISCELLANEOUS INFORMATION CONCERNING",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Dear Sir:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "Mrs. [REDACTED] Richmond, b7c",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Virginia, advised this office on January 2, 1957, that she",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "had received a letter from captioned organization requesting",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "she furnish any information she might have relative to her",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "alleged observation of a \"flying saucer\" a year or so ago",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "near Richmond, Virginia. Mrs. [REDACTED] informed she is employed b7c",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "by the Richmond Quartermaster Depot of the United States",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Army and it was while on her way to work one morning that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "she had sighted the object in question. She stated that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "several other women employees of the Depot were present",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "and subsequently one of these women had told a newspaper",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "reporter about the incident and all their names had appeared",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "in the papers.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "Mrs. [REDACTED] advised that she was reluctant to answer b7c",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "the letter as she felt it could be an illegal or subversive",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "group who was trying to obtain information they should not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "have. She pointed out that she knew nothing about the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "organization but the correspondence did not reflect the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "group was connected with the United States Government in any",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "way.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "She informed that the letter indicated the group",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "was a national organization whose duty it was to investigate",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "any and all unusual aerial phenomenon. It also reflected",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "that one Bob Gribble was the Executive Director and Jim",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "Ewart was the Director of Investigations. The address for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "this organization was shown to be 5108 Finlay Street, Seattle,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "Washington.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
